{title:THE GIVING SONG}
{key:C}



There's a [C]joy in [C7]giving and I've [F]found it to be [D7]true,

The [G7]more you give to Jesus,

the [C]more He's gonna [F]give to [C]you,

So [C]give 'till you can't give [C7]anymore,

Give [F]more than you can [D7]afford,

And you'll [G7]find your cup will overflow,

